{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embrace your inner demon or be consumed by it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">17-year-old Polly escapes a nightmarish shelter, only to find herself trapped in the underworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The city was shrouded in fog. Deadly fog. If you see such a sign, be careful. Your fog bracelet will illuminate the deadly fog red when it's very close.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/descript6.png?t=1734006192\" />You'll encounter denizens of the otherworldly realm, not all against you, but none on your side. No matter how events unfold, never forget the terms of the pact that plunged you into this abyss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/descript.png?t=1734006192\" />Prepare for a unique gameplay experience, blending world exploration with battles from side and top-down perspectives. Ancient forbidden knowledge will bolster your strength. With each new spell mastered, Polly's power grows deadlier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/extras/descript4.png?t=1734006192\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore eerie realms, confront haunting figures from Polly's past, and master forbidden spells in a fight for freedom. Will you escape, or will the demon claim you first?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734006192","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/page.bg.jpg?t=1734006192","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598780/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734006192","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic